This project is important for the following reasons:

	1. Consumer Behavior: The mobile phone market is highly competitive, and consumers are always looking for the best value for their money. By predicting the price range category of mobile phones, you can help consumers make informed decisions about which phone to buy based on their budget and preferences.

	2. Market Analysis: Accurately predicting the price range of mobile phones can also provide valuable insights into the mobile phone market. By analyzing the features and specifications of different phones across different price ranges, you can identify trends in the market and determine what features are most important to consumers at different price points.

	3. Business Strategy: For mobile phone manufacturers and retailers, predicting the price range category of mobile phones can be critical for developing their business strategy. By understanding the market demand for phones at different price points, they can adjust their pricing and product offerings accordingly.
